name: Umcebo (Treasure Snake)
shortLoreBlurb: Umcebo (Treasure Snake) is a spirit/creature from Zulu/Xhosa associated with wealth serpent, water. Serpents mark thresholds and hidden wisdom. Appeased for safe passage and rains.
